    <center>
        <h1>God of War Ragnarok</h1>
        <img src="~/Images/god of war.jpg" alt="war" style="width:700px">
        <p>
            God of War 2018 was nothing short of a masterpiece, a thrilling story, exciting enemies and more
            importantly fun as hell gamplay that offered new thrills while staying true to the God of War combat formaula
