            Get ready for more chaotic gameplay against crazy looking enemies and over the top combat with
            <b>Bayonetta 3.</b> Created by Paltinum Games and published by Nintendo they bring you back this
            beloved series with its third installment which promises over the top action segments you come to know
            and love from any Platinum Games title. Come by and check out the title yourself with the sneak peak!
        </p>
    </center>
    <br />

