            title StarField. StarField will let you live out your space dreams by travelling to distant worlds,
            fight off space bandits or aliens, use all sorts of unique guns and gadgets to defeat your oponents,
            even customize your personal aircraft to survive the vacuum of space and defeat other ships in epic
